div.div: The second season of Tonikaku Kawaii. The sweet story of Nasa and Tsukasa continues! After surviving some awkward first nights together, dealing with doubters, and recovering from their apartment fire, it's clear the fate of these lovers was written in the stars. Now, they're ready to settle back into domestic bliss and finally plan their wedding ceremony! But with plenty of new friends on the way, what will their big day look like?! (Source: Crunchyroll)

With graduation right around the corner, every member of the Light Music Club except for Azusa will be leaving for good. But the girls arent going to let something as silly as graduation tear them apart! For their final hurrah, the girls are going on the ultimate vacation tour all the way to London! Their overseas journey will lead them on a trip of discovery and friendship as they take the stage one last time for their final encore together. (Source: Sentai Filmworks)
Kimi wa Yakamashi Tojite yo Kuchi wo!

Childhood friends who've been together forever since they were little. Although they've noticed their feelings for each other, they're too close to be honest. What links them is the "I love you game" they have been playing since they were little. The conclusion to their love has been entrusted to this petty game, where winning means making the other person feel embarrassed.
(Source: Shogakukan, translated)
